text: Tim Goodbody (born 1983) is an Irish sailor. He competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics in Beijing, where he placed 21st in the Finn class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Ireland Category:Sailors at the 2008 Summer Olympics – Finn
